I Media Works]]|page=176|isbn=4-7572-0168-0|language=Japanese|date=1998}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Sakura2setting\">{{cite book|script-title=ja:\u30b5\u30af\u30e9\u5927\u62262 \u541b\u3001\u6b7b\u306b\u305f\u3082\u3046\u3053\u3068\u306a\u304b\u308c \u539f\u753b&\u8a2d\u5b9a\u8cc7\u6599\u96c6|trans-title=Sakura Wars 2: Thou Shalt Not Die Original Picture & Setting Material Collection|publisher=[[SB Creative|SoftBank Creative]]|isbn=4-7973-0755-2|language=Japanese|date=1998|page=130}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SakuraGameplayMag\">{{cite journal|script-title=ja:\u30b5\u30af\u30e9\u5927\u6226 Special Report|trans-title=Sakura Wars Special Report|journal=Sega Saturn Magazine|publisher=[[SB Creative|SoftBank Creative]]|issue=Vol 17|date=October 11, 1996|pages=37\u201341|language=Japanese}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SakuraDorimanga\">{{cite journal | date=June 13, 2003 | script-title=ja:\u521d\u9854\u5408\u308f\u305b! \u3068\u3063\u3066\u304a\u304d\u306e\u5bfe\u8ac7\u5e83\u4e95\u738b\u5b50\u00d7\u5c0f\u5cf6\u79c0\u592b |trans-title=My first meeting! My favorite talk with Hiroi Oji \u00d7 Hideo Kojima| journal=Dorimaga | issue=Vol 12 | publisher=[[SB Creative|SoftBank Creative]]| language=Japanese}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SakuraGemaga\">{{cite journal | date=March 29, 2008 | script-title=ja:\u30b5\u30af\u30e9\u5927\u6226 | trans-title=Sakura Wars |  journal=Gemaga | issue=May 2008 | publisher=[[SB Creative|SoftBank Creative]]| language=Japanese}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SSMinterview\">{{cite magazine | date=December 27, 1996 | script-title=ja:\u300c\u30b5\u30af\u30e9\u5927\u6226\u300d\u5e1d\u56fd\u6b4c\u5287\u56e3\u30fb\u97f3\u697d\u306e\u30eb\u30fc\u30c4\u306b\u8ffd\u308b!! | trans-title=Follow the roots of the \"Sakura Wars\" Imperial Combat Revue's Music!! |magazine=Sega Saturn Magazine |volume=22 | publisher=[[SB Creative|SoftBank Creative]]| language=Japanese}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SSMinterview2\">{{cite magazine | date=April 12, 1996 | script-title=ja:\u30b5\u30af\u30e9\u5927\u6226 | tr