ra Wars Anime Website|date=2000|access-date=May 7, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070114205718/http://www.mbs.jp/sakura/Report2.html|archive-date=January 14, 2007|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SakuraOVA\">{{cite web|url=https://www.bandaivisual.co.jp/cont/item/BCBA-0041/|script-title=ja:\u30b5\u30af\u30e9\u5927\u6226 \uff5e\u685c\u83ef\u7d62\u721b\uff5e\u3000DVD COLLECTION|trans-title=Sakura Wars: The Gorgeous Blooming Cherry Blossoms- DVD Collection|language=Japanese|publisher=[[Bandai Visual]]|access-date=May 7, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170507180134/https://www.bandaivisual.co.jp/cont/item/BCBA-0041/|archive-date=May 7, 2017|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SilInfoTanaka\">{{cite web|url=https://www.siliconera.com/2019/03/31/project-sakura-wars-introduces-its-fresh-cast-of-combat-revue-members/|title=Project Sakura Wars Introduces Its Fresh Cast Of Combat Revue Members|author=Wong, Alistair|website=Siliconera|publisher=Curse LLC|date=March 31, 2019|access-date=April 15, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402054959/https://www.siliconera.com/2019/03/31/project-sakura-wars-introduces-its-fresh-cast-of-combat-revue-members/|archive-date=April 2, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SakuraRating2006\">{{cite magazine|url=http://www.next-gen.biz/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=2401&Itemid=2|title=Japan Votes on All Time Top 100|author=Campbell, Colin|magazine=[[Edge (magazine)|Edge]]|publisher=[[Future plc]]|date=March 3, 2006|access-date=May 7, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060420181100/http://www.next-gen.biz/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=2401&Itemid=2|archive-date=April 20, 2006|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SakuraFanTranslation\">{{cite web|url=https://www.siliconera.com/sega-saturn-sakura-wars-fan-translation-is-completed-and-now-available/|title=Sega Saturn Sakura Wars Fan Translation Is Completed And Now Available|last=Wong|first=Alistair|we