p.com/news/snake-beats-mario-coolest-video |title=Snake Beats Mario, Is Coolest Video Game Character Ever |author=Glifford, Kevin |website=[[1UP.com]] |access-date=March 10, 2010 |date=February 10, 2010 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5sb1C6bP1?url=http://www.1up.com/news/snake-beats-mario-coolest-video |archive-date=September 8, 2010 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"KotakuSakura\">{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/poll-japans-most-memorable-games-on-each-console-1780043369|title=Poll: Japans Most Memorable Games on Each Console|author=Ashcraft, Brian|website=[[Kotaku]]|publisher=[[G/O Media]]|date=June 2, 2016|access-date=May 7, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170430223647/http://kotaku.com/poll-japans-most-memorable-games-on-each-console-1780043369|archive-date=April 30, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SakuraPXZa\">{{cite web|url=http://andriasang.com/con111/chunli_project_x_zone/|title=Chun-Li and Morrigan Join the Cast of Project X Zone|access-date=August 12, 2012|author=Gantayat, Anoop|publisher=Andriasang|date=May 16, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303235513/http://andriasang.com/con111/chunli_project_x_zone/|archive-date=March 3, 2016|url-status=dead|df=}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SakuraPXZb\">{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/the-56-playable-characters-in-project-x-zone-2-1743472346|title=The 58 Playable Characters in Project X Zone 2|author=Eisenbeis, Richard|website=[[Kotaku]]|publisher=[[G/O Media]]|date=November 20, 2015|access-date=May 7, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161023185104/http://kotaku.com/the-56-playable-characters-in-project-x-zone-2-1743472346|archive-date=October 23, 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SakuraOVAadv\">{{cite web|url=http://www.sakurawarsdvd.com/performances/anime.shtml|title=Sakura Wars - Performances|publisher=[[A.D. Vision]]|access-date=April 1, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050316114441/http://www.sakurawarsdvd.com/performan